      "content": "he says he's fine though, just really sleepy. he's been drinking a lot of water and trying to nap it off. could it just be dehydration or maybe just the cabin pressure messing with him? i dont want to freak him out and make him go to the hospital for nothing if it's just travel fatigue.",
